Hey all,

Based on some feedback, I decided to make an "EmptyExperiment" he=
ader and source file.  These are useful for people creating their own exper=
iments in HyperNEAT C++ because it allows people to see how an experiment w=
orks without conflating the general experiment details with how to play che=
ckers or compare boxes.

The empty experiments will be added to HyperNEAT 3=
.0 in the next couple of days, but here is a draft version:

ucf.edu/~jgauci/Releases/HCUBE_EmptyExperiment.h
